parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Engine failure can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls without warning
the engine loses power
the check oil warning indicator illuminates
the engine power loss indicator illuminates
smoke and fire come from the undercarriage.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Cam shaft failure can cause the engine to destroy itself, leading to costly repairs and potentially leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The cam shaft fractures internally
the cam followers fall off
the engine assembly is destroyed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: High pressure fuel pump failure can cause the engine to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine power loss indicator illuminates
the engine stalls and loses power
a loud pop sound is heard.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Computer scanner system failure can cause the engine to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The engine light illuminates
the vehicle stalls
the computer scanner system sends incorrect readings to the engine.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the turbocharger can cause a loss of motive power, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Abnormal sound coming from the engine compartment
turbocharger needle on the instrument cluster falls to zero
loss of motive power while depressing the accelerator pedal
abnormal banging sound
power steering failure.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the engine can cause a loss of motive power, making it difficult to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: Abnormal sound coming from the engine compartment
loss of motive power while depressing the accelerator pedal
abnormal banging sound
power steering failure
vehicle stalls.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The uncommanded engine stalling on inclines can cause the vehicle to lose power and roll backwards, potentially leading to accidents, injuries, or fatalities.
symptoms: The engine stalls without warning while driving up a hill
the vehicle loses power and rolls backwards
the brakes are unable to stop the vehicle due to lack of power.
